               </span>              </div>            </span>            <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>            <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                      </div>                                        <div id="js_tags" class="article-tag__list" style="display: none;" data-len="0">                                        <div class="article-tag-card__title">收录于合集</div>              <div class="article-tags">                              </div>                      </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-ratio="1.5" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style="height: auto !important;" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/U5fBOaXlIQmBs8DzQK41yLhG1p4zNdiaEj8GbJhcyPmWt7iaD0UQXy4eGya9gk4xYrXiajlmCT5E0uaDvn33kXnQQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg"></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">在体制内工作，业务能力不是第一位，社交能力才是第一位。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这是很多人的共识，也是很多人的困惑。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">为什么在体制内，不是业务能力最强的人最得领导青睐，而是最会说话的人得到重用？</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">为什么在体制内，不是最有能力的人做决策，而是最有关系的人掌握话语权？</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这些问题，其实都可以从社交能力的角度来解释。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">社交能力，简单来说，就是与他人沟通交流的能力。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">它包括了很多方面，比如说话的技巧、情商的高低、人际关系的处理、团队协作的能力等。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">社交能力不仅仅是一种技能，更是一种素质，一种态度，一种人生哲学。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">在体制内工作，社交能力尤为重要。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">因为体制内的环境往往比较复杂，有很多规则、利益、权力、关系等等需要考虑。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">如果没有良好的社交能力，就很难在体制内立足，更不用说发展了。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">社交能力可以帮助你建立良好的人际关系。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">在体制内工作，你不可能一个人独立完成所有的任务，你需要和同事、上司、下属、合作伙伴等各种人打交道。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">如果你有良好的社交能力，你就可以和他们沟通顺畅，建立信任和尊重，互相支持和帮助，形成一个和谐的工作氛围。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这样不仅可以提高工作效率和质量，也可以增加工作乐趣和满意度。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">社交能力可以帮助你提升自己的影响力。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">在体制内工作，你不可能只靠自己的能力来取得成就，你需要让别人认可你的价值和贡献，给你足够的机会和资源。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">如果你有良好的社交能力，你就可以通过说服、沟通、协商等方式来影响他人的思想和行为，让他们支持你的观点和建议，赞同你的决策和方案，配合你的计划和安排。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这样不仅可以增加你的权威和地位，也可以扩大你的发展空间。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">社交能力可以帮助你应对各种挑战和困难。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">在体制内工作，你不可能避免遇到各种问题和风险，比如竞争、冲突、压力、变化等等。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">如果你有良好的社交能力，你就可以通过合作、协调、调解等方式来解决问题和化解风险，让各方面都达到一个平衡和共赢的状态。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这样不仅可以保护自己的利益和声誉，也可以维护体制内的稳定和发展。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">总之，在体制内工作，社交能力是第一位的。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这并不是说其他方面的能力就不重要了，而是说社交能力是其他方面能力发挥效果的前提和保障。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "Helvetica Neue";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">如果你想在体制内有所作为，就要提高自己的社交能力，在复杂多变的环境中，用智慧和技巧来赢得尊重和信任，用影响力和资源来实现目标和愿望，用合作和协调来应对挑战和困难。</span></p><p style='font-variant-numeric: normal;font-variant-east-asian: normal;font-variant-alternates: normal;font-kerning: auto;font-optical-sizing: auto;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-variant-position: normal;font-stretch: normal;font-size: 13px;font-family: "PingFang SC";color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-wrap: wrap;'><span style="font-size: 17px;">这样，你就可以在体制内工作中，不仅生存，而且发展，不仅平安，而且成功。</span></p><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="3"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="1717161811" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>              </div>    </div>]]></description>
